{"tid":1076470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港仔男子疑因病厭世 公園留遺書吊頸亡","createTime":"2019-03-25T01:12:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T01:36:54.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4455885d4f11cc98767da4f00120c80dffe23635","tid":1076470,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:12:01.000Z","msg":"香港仔華富邨華康樓對開公園，早上6時許，一名姓黃33歲男子，被晨運客發現在涼亭上吊頸，昏迷不醒，大驚立刻報警，消防員到場剪斷麻繩將男子解下，惟救護員證實他已氣絕身亡，警員用帳篷遮蓋屍體及展開調查，在死者身上發現證件及遺書，據悉，事主有身體病及情緒病紀錄，懷疑他因病厭世自殺，案件並無可疑。<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6S2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=d5b970d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190325/59408041\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190325%2F59408041&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6S2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=107823a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190325%2F59408041&h=4b01cf2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190325/59408041</a>"},{"pid":"12907e7a182dbfa00fe24aa360a68e162f020b3a","tid":1076470,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:15:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78f1bdb588c1838bdc4be1a6974553be105125d4","tid":1076470,"uid":84128,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:16:41.000Z","msg":"香港人口+149<br />\n大陸人+150<br />\n本地人-1"},{"pid":"9c294739b160a27c529f03a438506e3d4e656e75","tid":1076470,"uid":19552,"like":1,"disli